  title: Improving your app by using engagement loops
  descriptionInMd: We use a game design model called ‘engagement loops’ to design products and services that are awesome and interesting. This model revolves around identifying a meaningful challenge, something that your users actually want to become better at (like learning a language, becoming healthier etc.). We then help them improve on the challenge by adding game-like structures and rich feedback around that challenge. This way we create a feedback loop that keeps users coming back because they want to.
